  "markdown": "Anyon Systems Inc. \u00b7 Montr\u00e9al \u00b7 A Canadian quantum company\n[](https://anyonsys.com/en)\n  * Company\n  * Markets\n  * [Products](https://anyonsys.com/en/products)\n  * [Technology](https://anyonsys.com/en/technology)\n  * [News](https://anyonsys.com/en/news)\n  * Careers\n  * FR\n\n\nFR[Contact](https://anyonsys.com/en/contact)\n# We\u2019re not scaling a company. We\u2019re scaling a new industry.\n## The Anyon Way\nAt Anyon, we\u2019re building quantum computing as **deployable infrastructure**. That means solving deeply technical challenges across physics, hardware, fabrication, and software, then turning them into systems that operate reliably outside the lab. Since 2014, we\u2019ve focused on execution as much as innovation, bringing together people who care about **precision, performance, and impact**. If you\u2019re motivated by complex systems, real constraints, and building technology that **actually gets used** , you\u2019ll find the work here meaningful.\n![](https://anyonsys.com/assets/site-images/office-external/office-external-09.jpg?v=cfc17f3)\n  * 01\n### Real systems, not just experiments\nWe design, build, and deploy quantum computers into operational environments. The work is grounded in real constraints (thermal, electrical, mechanical, and computational) and measured by performance in the field.\n  * 02\n### Depth across disciplines\nOur systems sit at the intersection of superconducting physics, cryogenics, RF engineering, nanofabrication, high-performance computing, and software. You\u2019ll work across boundaries with people who bring deep expertise, and expect the same in return.\n  * 03\n### Engineering with rigour\nWe value disciplined engineering: repeatability, reliability, and manufacturability. Whether it\u2019s a quantum chip, a cryogenic subsystem, or control electronics, the goal is always the same: build it so it works, and keeps working.\n  * 04\n### Ownership at system level\nWork here is not abstracted. Teams take ownership of complete subsystems and their integration into the full stack. You see how decisions propagate, and you\u2019re accountable for outcomes.\n  * 05\n### Scale the technology, not just the team\nWe\u2019re moving from early deployments to broader adoption. That means scaling designs, processes, and systems, not just headcount. The problems evolve, and so does the impact.\n\n\n![Anyon Systems](https://anyonsys.com/assets/logo_pure-white.svg?v=cfc17f3)\nFull-stack superconducting quantum systems. Designed and built in Montr\u00e9al.\n  * [About](https://anyonsys.com/en/company/about)\n  * [News](https://anyonsys.com/en/news)\n  * [Careers](https://anyonsys.com/en/careers/jobs)\n\n\nMontr\u00e9al \u00b7 QC \u00b7 Canada\n[LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/company/anyon-systems-inc-/)\nMarkets\n  * [HPC centres](https://anyonsys.com/en/markets/hpc)\n  * [Government](https://anyonsys.com/en/markets/government)\n  * [Defence](https://anyonsys.com/en/markets/defence)\n  * [Universities](https://anyonsys.com/en/markets/research)\n\n\nProducts\n  * [Qube](https://anyonsys.com/en/products#qube)\n  * [Hudson](https://anyonsys.com/en/products#hudson)\n  * [Snowflurry](https://anyonsys.com/en/products#snowflurry)\n  * [Roadmap](https://anyonsys.com/en/products#roadmap)\n\n\nTechnology\n  * [Quantum processor](https://anyonsys.com/en/technology#quantum-processor)\n  * [Cryogenic system](https://anyonsys.com/en/technology#cryogenic-system)\n  * [Control electronics](https://anyonsys.com/en/technology#control-electronics)\n  * [Software stack](https://anyonsys.com/en/technology#software-stack)\n\n\nResources\n  * [Roadmap](https://anyonsys.com/en/products#roadmap)\n\n\nHead office\nMontr\u00e9al \u00b7 Quebec\n8275 Trans Canada Route A410\nSaint-Laurent, QC H4S 0B6\nQuebec\nBromont \u00b7 Quebec\n45 Bd de l\u2019A\u00e9roport\nBromont, QC J2L 2X4\nQuebec\nSherbrooke \u00b7 Quebec\n3000 Bd de l\u2019Universit\u00e9\nSherbrooke, QC J1K 0A5\nOntario\nWaterloo \u00b7 Ontario\n295 Hagey Blvd #2\nWaterloo, ON N2L 6R5\nUnited Kingdom\nKidlington\nOxford Technology Park, Technology Dr\nKidlington OX5 1GN\nIsrael\nIsrael\nAddress coming soon\n\u00a9 2026 Anyon Systems Inc.\n[Privacy](https://anyonsys.com/en/privacy)[Support](https://anyonsys.com/en/contact)\nTop\n## We use cookies!\nThis website uses cookies to enhance your experience.\nAccept allAccept only necessary\nManage preferences\n[Privacy Policy](https://anyonsys.com/en/privacy)\n",
