" aria-expanded=\"false\" data-base-ui-navigation-menu-trigger=\"\" class=\"font-ays-display text-sm font-medium hover:text-ays-brand transition-colors text-ays-ink/55 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-4 h-20 -my-4 cursor-pointer\">Markets<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"transition-transform duration-150 ease-out data-[popup-open]:rotate-180\"><svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" fill=\"none\" class=\"text-ays-ink/50\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 4l3 3 3-3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button></li><li><a href=\"/en/products\" class=\"font-ays-display text-sm font-medium hover:text-ays-brand transition-colors text-ays-ink/55 inline-flex items-center px-4 h-20 -my-4\">Products</a></li><li><a href=\"/en/technology\" class=\"font-ays-display text-sm font-medium hover:text-ays-brand transition-colors text-ays-ink/55 inline-flex items-center px-4 h-20 -my-4\">Technology</a></li><li><a href=\"/en/news\" class=\"font-ays-display text-sm font-medium hover:text-ays-brand transition-colors text-ays-ink/55 inline-flex items-center px-4 h-20 -my-4\">News</a></li><li><button type=\"button\" aria-disabled=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-expanded=\"false\" data-base-ui-navigation-menu-trigger=\"\" class=\"font-ays-display text-sm font-medium hover:text-ays-brand transition-colors text-ays-ink inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-4 h-20 -my-4 cursor-pointer\">Careers<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"transition-transform duration-150 ease-out data-[popup-open]:rotate-180\"><svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" fill=\"none\" class=\"text-ays-ink/50\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 4l3 3 3-3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button></li><li><button type=\"button\" aria-disabled=\"false\" aria-pressed=\"false\" aria-label=\"Switch to French\" class=\"cursor-pointer focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-ays-brand font-ays-display text-sm font-medium hover:text-ays-brand transition-colors text-ays-ink inline-flex items-center px-4\">FR</button></li></ul></nav><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><button type=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-pressed=\"false\" aria-label=\"Switch to French\" class=\"cursor-pointer focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-ays-brand font-ays-display text-sm font-medium hover:text-ays-brand transition-colors lg:hidden\">FR</button><a href=\"/en/contact\" class=\"group hidden sm:inline-flex items-center justify-center leading-3 gap-2 pl-3.5 pr-2 pt-3 pb-3 border border-ays-brand bg-ays-brand text-white font-ays-display text-sm font-normal tracking-tight hover:bg-white/75 hover:text-ays-brand transition-colors\">Contact<svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"relative shrink-0 top-px transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M6 4l4 4-4 4\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg></a><button type=\"button\" class=\"lg:hidden p-2 -mr-2 text-ays-ink\" aria-label=\"Menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 7h18M3 12h18M3 17h18\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg></button></div></div></header><div class=\"flex-1\"><section class=\"bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 pt-20 lg:pt-32 pb-20 lg:pb-28\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 w-full\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-9\"><h1 class=\"font-ays-display font-light tracking-ays-tightest leading-none text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl xl:text-8xl text-ays-ink\">We\u2019re not scaling a company. We\u2019re scaling<!-- --> <span class=\"text-ays-brand\">a new industry.</span></h1><h2 class=\"mt-12 lg:mt-16 font-ays-display font-light tracking-ays-tightest leading-[1.1] text-2xl lg:text-3xl text-ays-ink\">The Anyon Way</h2><p class=\"mt-6 lg:mt-8 max-w-[58ch] text-lg lg:text-xl text-ays-ink/70 leading-[1.55]\">At Anyon, we\u2019re building quantum computing as <strong class=\"font-bold text-ays-ink\">deployable infrastructure</strong>. That means solving deeply technical challenges across physics, hardware, fabrication, and software, then turning them into systems that operate reliably outside the lab. Since 2014, we\u2019ve focused on execution as much as innovation, bringing together people who care about <strong class=\"font-bold text-ays-ink\">precision, performance, and impact</strong>. If you\u2019re motivated by complex systems, real constraints, and building technology that <strong class=\"font-bold text-ays-ink\">actually gets used</strong>, you\u2019ll find the work here meaningful.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-ays-paper-light border-t ays-hairline\"><div class=\"max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-20 lg:py-28\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10 lg:gap-12\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden aspect-video lg:aspect-auto lg:col-span-1\"><img src=\"/assets/site-images/office-external/office-external-09.jpg?v=cfc17f3\" alt=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover\"></div><ul class=\"lg:col-span-2 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 lg:gap-x-16\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-6 py-8 lg:py-10 border-t ays-hairline\"><span class=\"hidden shrink-0 pt-1.5 font-ays-mono text-xs text-ays-mid tracking-ays-mono-wide\">01</span><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"font-ays-display text-xl lg:text-2xl text-ays-ink leading-snug\">Real systems, not just experiments</h3><p class=\"max-w-[52ch] text-base text-ays-ink/70 leading-relaxed\">We design, build, and deploy quantum computers into operational environments. The work is grounded in real constraints (thermal, electrical, mechanical, and computational) and measured by performance in the field.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-6 py-8 lg:py-10 border-t ays-hairline\"><span class=\"hidden shrink-0 pt-1.5 font-ays-mono text-xs text-ays-mid tracking-ays-mono-wide\">02</span><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"font-ays-display text-xl lg:text-2xl text-ays-ink leading-snug\">Depth across disciplines</h3><p class=\"max-w-[52ch] text-base text-ays-ink/70 leading-relaxed\">Our systems sit at the intersection of superconducting physics, cryogenics, RF engineering, nanofabrication, high-performance computing, and software. You\u2019ll work across boundaries with people who bring deep expertise, and expect the same in return.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-6 py-8 lg:py-10 border-t ays-hairline\"><span class=\"hidden shrink-0 pt-1.5 font-ays-mono text-xs text-ays-mid tracking-ays-mono-wide\">03</span><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"font-ays-display text-xl lg:text-2xl text-ays-ink leading-snug\">Engineering with rigour</h3><p class=\"max-w-[52ch] text-base text-ays-ink/70 leading-relaxed\">We value disciplined engineering: repeatability, reliability, and manufacturability. Whether it\u2019s a quantum chip, a cryogenic subsystem, or control electronics, the goal is always the same: build it so it works, and keeps working.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-6 py-8 lg:py-10 border-t ays-hairline\"><span class=\"hidden shrink-0 pt-1.5 font-ays-mono text-xs text-ays-mid tracking-ays-mono-wide\">04</span><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"font-ays-display text-xl lg:text-2xl text-ays-ink leading-snug\">Ownership at system level</h3><p class=\"max-w-[52ch] text-base text-ays-ink/70 leading-relaxed\">Work here is not abstracted. Teams take ownership of complete subsystems and their integration into the full stack. You see how decisions propagate, and you\u2019re accountable for outcomes.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-6 py-8 lg:py-10 border-t ays-hairline\"><span class=\"hidden shrink-0 pt-1.5 font-ays-mono text-xs text-ays-mid tracking-ays-mono-wide\">05</span><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"font-ays-display text-xl lg:text-2xl text-ays-ink leading-snug\">Scale the technology, not just the team</h3><p class=\"max-w-[52ch] text-base text-ays-ink/70 leading-relaxed\">We\u2019re moving from early deployments to broader adoption. That means scaling designs, processes, and systems, not just headcount. The problems evolve, and so does the impact.</p></div></li></ul></div></div></section></div><footer class=\"text-white\"><div class=\"bg-ays-ink\"><div class=\"max-w-ays-screen-2xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 pt-20 pb-16\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-8\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-4\"><img src=\"/assets/logo_pure-white.svg?v=cfc17f3\" alt=\"Anyon Systems\" class=\"h-10 w-auto\" width=\"4000\" height=\"800\"><p class=\"mt-6 text-white/70 leading-relaxed max-w-sm text-base\">Full-stack superconducting quantum systems. Designed and built in Montr\u00e9al.</p><ul class=\"mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-5 gap-y-2\"><li><a href=\"/en/company/about\" class=\"group inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-white/80 hover:text-white transition-colors\">About<svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 15 13\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5\"><path d=\"M6 4l4 4-4 4\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg></a></li><li><a href=\"/en/news\" class=\"group inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-white/80 hover:text-white transition-colors\">News<svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 15 13\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5\"><path d=\"M6 4l4 4-4 4\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg></a></li><li><a href=\"/en